Ubuntu Tweak 0.5.7
==================

* Overview of changes:
 - CategoryView: make Other always the last item
 - Add option to set Terminal menubar (Thanks DaNmarner)
 - Git rid of python-gnome2 (gnome.vfs and gnome.ui)

* Bugs fixed:
 - LP: #647996 Too long settings group title
 - Typo in Nautilus settings: priveleges -> privileges

Ubuntu Tweak 0.5.6
==================

* Overview of changes:
 - Move uturl, ubuntu-tweak-daemon to share folder again
 - Add reset feature for almost all Gconf related tweak options
 - File Type Manager: move the edit button to right-bottom
 - New Feature: Desktop Recovery to backup and recover settings with ease
 - Add more system information to help debug

* Bugs fixed:
 - Fix change background in Login Settings failed because of space in path
 - LP: #614832 ubuntu tweak won't disable fix root appearance
 - LP: #615849 Ubuntu tweak daemon fails to start - Ubuntu 10.04
 - LP: #615638 window manager settings failed
 - LP: #597719 cleaner.py does not open


