Ubuntu Tweak 0.5.4
==================

* Overview changes:
 - Add support for Singleton Ubuntu Tweak
 - Add two new options to tweak GDM
 - Force enable the stable source to make sure Ubuntu Tweak is always
   up-to-date
 - Add support for Linux Mint 9
 - Add the feature to temporary disable PPA sources while refreshing
 - Only active compiz plugin when request
 - Add feature to enable the disabled third-party sources
 - Learn from Condult, add logging system
 - Add Login Settings to tweak GDM theme(Logo and background)

* Bugs fixed:
 - LP: #546331 Empty places in the list while deleting sources file
 - LP: #540215 Link failed with Permission denied
 - LP: #568454 The feature on "change the main menu icon" does not work in my
   lucid
 - LP: #564942 Default Folder Locations does not expose input method


